10 am – 7:30 pm
July 20 - July 23, 2017
July 25 - August 6, 2017
August 9 - August 16, 2017
August 18 - August 21, 2017
August 23 - August 27, 2017
August 29 - September 9, 2017
 


Museum in Virginia
There are no extended hours scheduled for the Steven F. Udvar-Hazy Center for the Spring or Summer.





























