“Breathtaking”


Reviewed July 20, 2012




This museum is awesome. It costs $15 to park, but if you go after 4? pm it's free. It's a very large hanger full of planes, missiles, and the Discovery shuttle. It was worth the time. The observation deck closes before the muesum though, so check the times and don't miss it - I did so looks like I have to go back ;).




Visited June 2012



